        FLAGS['BASIC_AUTH_ENABLED'][0]['value'] ^
        FLAGS['SSO_ENABLED'][0]['value']):
    raise ImproperlyConfigured(
        'Exactly one of BASIC_AUTH_ENABLED, SSO_ENABLED should be enabled.')
